message:
Command `curl -X POST -H "Authorization: token $GITHUB_TOKEN" \
-H "Accept: application/vnd.github.v3+json" \
--max-time 30 \
https://api.github.com/repos/sheepdestroyer/SheepVibes/pulls \
-d '{
  "title": "feat: Add code review cycle microagent",
  "head": "feat/code-review-cycle-microagent",
  "base": "main",
  "body": "## Description\n\nThis PR adds a new microagent for handling iterative code review cycles.",
  "draft": false
}'` executed with exit code 0.

message.content: Now let me try to create the PR using curl with a timeout to avoid hanging.
